data.description: New paint, roof updated and this home is ready for new owners! This home sits in a quiet neighborhood, close to GVR centers and walking trails. The home has nice mountain views from the front enclosed porch and also through the large living room window. Inside the home has a spacious open living space, with laminate floors and a beautiful wood/gas burning fireplace. The kitchen has newly painted cabinets, and all appliances. There is a large addition in the back which can be used as a flex space with a private en-suite bathroom.  Two bedrooms at the other end of the home give you many options for den or office space. This home is being sold AS-IS. What a great opportunity to own a home in Green Valley.
